title: Switches as GridLayout (slight spacing fixes)
message:
Switches as GridLayout (slight spacing fixes)

Changed `[RC]Switches` `RelativeLayout` to 3 by 2 `GridLayout`.
On my devices, this version lines up nicely, and provides a bit more
space on smaller screens.

title: hotfix: prevent NPE crash on rotation
message:
hotfix: prevent NPE crash on rotation

Checks whether `key` is `null` and if yes bypasses login check.
This will likely have unintended consequences, but at least the
app doesn't crash on rotation, and seems to work fine.
